flowchart TD
    Start([Start Program]) --> Init[Initialize Organization]
    Init --> ConnectDB[Connect to SQLite Database]
    ConnectDB --> CreateTables[Create Tables if Not Exist]
    CreateTables --> LoadData[Load Data from Database]
    LoadData --> LoadEmp[Load Employees]
    LoadEmp --> LoadDept[Load Departments]
    LoadDept --> LoadProj[Load Projects]
    LoadProj --> LoadEquip[Load Equipment]
    LoadEquip --> DisplayMenu[Display Main Menu]

    DisplayMenu --> GetChoice{User Choice}

    GetChoice -->|1| EmpMenu[Employee Management Menu]
    GetChoice -->|2| DeptMenu[Department Management Menu]
    GetChoice -->|3| ProjMenu[Project Management Menu]
    GetChoice -->|4| EquipMenu[Equipment Management Menu]
    GetChoice -->|5| SearchMenu[Search Operations Menu]
    GetChoice -->|6| SortMenu[Sort Operations Menu]
    GetChoice -->|7| ReportMenu[Reports & Statistics Menu]
    GetChoice -->|0| CloseDB[Close Database Connection]
    GetChoice -->|Invalid| ErrorMsg[Display Error Message]

    EmpMenu --> EmpOperations[Add/Remove/View Employees]
    EmpOperations --> SaveEmp[Save to Database]
    SaveEmp --> DisplayMenu

    DeptMenu --> DeptOperations[Add/View Departments]
    DeptOperations --> SaveDept[Save to Database]
    SaveDept --> DisplayMenu

    ProjMenu --> ProjOperations[Add/View Projects]
    ProjOperations --> SaveProj[Save to Database]
    SaveProj --> DisplayMenu

    EquipMenu --> EquipOperations[Add/Assign Equipment]
    EquipOperations --> SaveEquip[Save to Database]
    SaveEquip --> DisplayMenu

    SearchMenu --> SearchOps[Linear/Binary Search]
    SearchOps --> DisplayResults[Display Search Results]
    DisplayResults --> DisplayMenu

    SortMenu --> SortOps[Bubble/Quick Sort]
    SortOps --> DisplaySorted[Display Sorted List]
    DisplaySorted --> DisplayMenu

    ReportMenu --> GenReports[Generate Statistics]
    GenReports --> DisplayStats[Display Reports]
    DisplayStats --> DisplayMenu

    ErrorMsg --> DisplayMenu
    CloseDB --> End([Exit Program])

